{"tid":1960723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【抗暴之戰】蒙面法實施後五男女涉屯門堵路被控 有被告投訴遭操普通話蒙面警毆打","createTime":"2020-04-06T10:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T10:52:53.000Z","uid":23833,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2f409c276c0879f95b6127ca7c2be7c340034317","tid":1960723,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:27:05.000Z","msg":"《禁止蒙面規例》去年10月5日實施，但無阻市民上街反抗暴政。五名男女涉於規例實施後第三天晚上，用竹枝及木梯等堵塞屯門鄉事會路，並涉嫌攜帶載有黑色液體的氣球，意圖損壞他人財產。事隔近半年，五人被控在公眾地方造成阻礙等罪，案件今在沙田裁判法院提堂。有被告投訴被捕後遭一名操普通話的蒙面警員施襲，另有警員用手踭襲擊他已受傷的口部，且羈押期間不獲送院。案件5月25日再訊，被告全獲准保釋候訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五被告依次為女學生甘嫚婷（21歲）、17歲蔣姓男學生、男學生布凱軒（19歲）、男學生曾錫希（19歲）及男裝修工人趙展東（27歲）。他們共同被控一項在公眾地方造成阻礙罪，控罪指他們於去年10月7日與其他不知名人士，在屯門青山公路新墟段與鄉事會路交界，留下四根竹棍、兩把木梯及一把太陽傘，使在該地點的人或車輛受到阻礙、不便或威脅。<br />\n首被告另被指於同日同地，保管一些裝有黑色液體的氣球、一些空的氣球及一瓶黑色液體，意圖使用該些物品破壞另一人的財產，被控管有物品意圖破壞財產罪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200406/3VJMW3L5ECBISCQDZEOGI2UY5Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200406%2F3VJMW3L5ECBISCQDZEOGI2UY5Q%2F&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLXQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=d7f6c2a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200406%2F3VJMW3L5ECBISCQDZEOGI2UY5Q%2F&h=b2e09a33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200406/3VJMW3L5ECBISCQDZEOGI2UY5Q/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b90a8fac801869b8a7ae98d47f170dd3dd67fd59","tid":1960723,"uid":23833,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:27:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffefd62897f8607547ca612cb796f51cf7b73f88","tid":1960723,"uid":165028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:28:11.000Z","msg":"點解十幾歲就反抗"},{"pid":"7259e59249016b90a6d0134e6f523ee49f9f868c","tid":1960723,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T10:52:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}